<header class="bg-color hero pa3 pa4-m pa5-l lh-title" aria-labelledby="page-title">
  <div class="hero__content">
    <h1 id="page-title" class="f5 f4-m f3-l normal-ns"><%= data.site.meta.author %> is a designer & developer</h1>
    <p class="pt3 pt4-ns f3 f2-m f1-l normal i">With an interest in accessibility and usability, he's trying to make the web a better place for everyone; he also dislikes talking about himself in third person, and spends too much time thinking about fictional characters</p>
    <p><a class="jump" href="#content">Jump to introduction</a></p>
  </div>
</header>

<div id="content">
  <section class="pt3 pt4-m pt5-l mh3 mb3 mh4-m mb4-m mh5-l mb5-l" aria-labelledby="intro-title">
    <header class="hidden" aria-labelledby="intro-title">
      <h2 id="intro-title">An introduction</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="mw7 center">
      <p class="measure mb3">Yup, that's me &ndash; <a href="about">I'm Oscar</a>! I've been tinkering with the web for more than a decade now, and I love it more than ever. It's really what pushed me towards bettering myself in all aspects of design and development, and because of this, between 2016 and 2019, I was an informatics student at <a href="//www.hb.se" hreflang="sv" lang="sv">Högskolan&nbsp;i&nbsp;Borås</a>.</p>
      <p class="measure mb3">In the months leading up to the summer of 2019, I was primarily researching for and writing on my final thesis together with a friend. The thesis can be described as an exploration and evaluation of accessibility in relation to websites for institutions of higher education in Sweden</p>
      <p class="measure">This August, however, I will be joining <a href="https://www.botek.se">Botek</a> as a systems developer and will hopefully be involved in many different parts of their software development processes &ndash; yay! <span class="emoji__aria" role="img" aria-label="Smiling face" tabindex="0">&#x1f604;</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ma3 ma4-m ma5-l" aria-labelledby="items-title">
    <header class="mw7 center mb3 mb4-ns" aria-labelledby="items-title">
      <h2 id="items-title" class="f4 f3-ns lh-solid">I'm currently<sup class="sup"><a href="#note">&ast;</a></sup>&hellip;</h2>
    </header>

    <ul class="items list mw8 pl0 center cf">
      <% data.media.currently.each do |media|
           subtitle = "<a href=\"#{media.url}\">#{media.subtitle}</a>"
           subtitle = "<cite>#{subtitle}</cite>" if media.cite
      %>
        <li class="items__item mb3 mb0-ns fl-ns">
          <h3 class="items__title mb2 mb3-ns f5 f4-ns lh-solid"><span class="emoji" role="img"><%= media.emoji %></span> <%= subtitle %></h3>
          <p class="pl4 pl0-ns"><%= media.description %></p>
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>

    <p id="note" class="mw7 center mt0 mb3 mv4-m mv5-l f6 f5-ns i">Well, I hope I'm doing any of those things&hellip; and if I'm not, I probably did within the last day or so.</p>
  </section>
</div>
